multisite.accuracy v1.2 (Release date: 2024-07-31)
========================================

Changes:

* Removed dependency on AROC package (scheduled for archival) by temporarily
  adapting the AROC.sp function (until the AROC package is on CRAN again).


multisite.accuracy v1.2 (Release date: 2023-04-18)
========================================

Changes:

* Solved an issue when using factors with "bac".


multisite.accuracy v1.1 (Release date: 2022-05-04)
========================================

Changes:

* When the estimate is "bac" (balanced accuracy), "y" may now be a factor
  (instead of a binary vector).


multisite.accuracy v1.0 (Release date: 2021-05-27)
========================================

First version.

